{"title":"春的辩证","authors":["易仁寰"],"dates":[{"year":1995,"month":3,"day":13}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"春的辩证"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"易仁寰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"佼佼者报春"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"郁郁者惜春"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闲适者迷于赏春"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赶路人忙于争春……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春呵，春——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你能溶雪化冰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"酿成一泻千里的奔腾；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你却又造成泥泞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陷住那步履维艰的负重……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你能以无声的滋润，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"染绿千万顷憧憬；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你也能以缠绵的潮湿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"霉变徘徊者的低吟……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那灿灿的春晓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"催醒远涉的驼铃；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而沉沉的春眠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又困倒懈怠的光阴……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春的犁杖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"耕耘着壮丽的艰辛；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春的飞絮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却托不起长长的雁阵……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春雨丝丝——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能缝合天与地，海和云，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能缝合昼与夜，远和近……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎样才能缝合"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两峰之间的低谷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战旗上面的弹孔？！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你精于预言，却不会算命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你种植期盼，却疏于收成；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你如期而至，岁岁枯荣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你来也匆匆，去也匆匆……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，多情的春，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无情的春，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫徘徊，莫悭吝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请把春的钥匙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"交给我们！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}